OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a cloudy start with
OL,6,Foutbreaks of rain, then becoming dry
OL,7,Fthrough the morning. Mainly dry with
OL,8,Fsunny spells in the afternoon.
OL,9,FModerate to fresh southwesterly winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA mainly dry, bright but
OL,12,Frather cloudy evening. The rest of the
OL,13,Fnight will remain dry with lengthy
OL,14,Fclear spells. Moderate to fresh
OL,15,Fsouthwesterly winds.
OL,16,
OL,17,CTuesday:FLengthy sunny spells between
OL,18,Fpatchy amounts of cloud. Most places
OL,19,Fwill remain dry, but the odd light
OL,20,Fpassing shower for Shetland is
OL,21,Fpossible. Fresh westerly winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
