OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FMainly
OL,6,Fdry with bright spells or sunny
OL,7,Fspells, risk of showers on Friday.
OL,8,FGentle winds on Wednesday but breezier
OL,9,Fon Thursday and Friday.
